#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animatedtexture.rst:19
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"``AnimatedTexture`` is a resource format for frame-based animations, "
"where multiple textures can be chained automatically with a predefined "
"delay for each frame. Unlike :ref:`AnimationPlayer "
"<class_AnimationPlayer>` or :ref:`AnimatedSprite <class_AnimatedSprite>`,"
" it isn't a :ref:`Node <class_Node>`, but has the advantage of being "
"usable anywhere a :ref:`Texture2D <class_Texture2D>` resource can be "
"used, e.g. in a :ref:`TileSet <class_TileSet>`."
msgstr ""
"``AnimatedTexture`` 是一种基于帧动画的资源格式，其中可以为每个帧预定义延迟，从而自动链接多个纹理。与 "
":ref:`AnimationPlayer <class_AnimationPlayer>` 或 :ref:`AnimatedSprite "
"<class_AnimatedSprite>` 不同，它不是一个 :ref:`Node "
"<class_Node>`，但具有的优势是，可以在任何可以使用 :ref:`Texture <class_Texture>` "
"资源的地方使用，例如，在 :ref:`TileSet <class_TileSet>` 中。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animatedtexture.rst:21
msgid ""
"The playback of the animation is controlled by the :ref:`fps "
"<class_AnimatedTexture_property_fps>` property as well as each frame's "
"optional delay (see :ref:`set_frame_delay "
"<class_AnimatedTexture_method_set_frame_delay>`). The animation loops, "
"i.e. it will restart at frame 0 automatically after playing the last "
"frame."
msgstr ""
"动画的播放由 :ref:`fps <class_AnimatedTexture_property_fps>` 属性，以及每个帧的可选延迟（参见 "
":ref:`set_frame_delay "
"<class_AnimatedTexture_method_set_frame_delay>`）控制。动画循环播放，即它将在播放最后一帧后，自动从第0帧重新开始。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animatedtexture.rst:23
msgid ""
"``AnimatedTexture`` currently requires all frame textures to have the "
"same size, otherwise the bigger ones will be cropped to match the "
"smallest one. Also, it doesn't support :ref:`AtlasTexture "
"<class_AtlasTexture>`. Each frame needs to be separate image."
msgstr ""
"``AnimatedTexture`` 当前要求所有帧的纹理，具有相同的大小，否则较大的纹理将被裁剪以匹配最小的纹理。另外，它不支持 "
":ref:`AtlasTexture <class_AtlasTexture>`。每个帧需要是单独的图像。"

