#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animatedtexture.rst:69
msgid ""
"Animation speed in frames per second. This value defines the default time"
" interval between two frames of the animation, and thus the overall "
"duration of the animation loop based on the :ref:`frames "
"<class_AnimatedTexture_property_frames>` property. A value of 0 means no "
"predefined number of frames per second, the animation will play according"
" to each frame's frame delay (see :ref:`set_frame_delay "
"<class_AnimatedTexture_method_set_frame_delay>`)."
msgstr ""
"动画速度，以每秒帧数为单位。该值定义了动画的两个帧之间的默认时间间隔，并因此，动画循环的整体持续时间，基于 :ref:`frames "
"<class_AnimatedTexture_property_frames>` "
"属性。值为0表示没有预定义每秒帧数，动画将根据每个帧的帧延迟播放（请参阅 :ref:`set_frame_delay "
"<class_AnimatedTexture_method_set_frame_delay>`）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animatedtexture.rst:71
msgid ""
"For example, an animation with 8 frames, no frame delay and a ``fps`` "
"value of 2 will run for 4 seconds, with each frame lasting 0.5 seconds."
msgstr "例如，具有8帧、无帧延迟、且 ``fps`` 值为2的动画，将运行4秒，每帧持续0.5秒。"

