#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animatedtexture.rst:129
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Assigns a :ref:`Texture2D <class_Texture2D>` to the given frame. Frame "
"IDs start at 0, so the first frame has ID 0, and the last frame of the "
"animation has ID :ref:`frames <class_AnimatedTexture_property_frames>` - "
"1."
msgstr ""
"给给定的帧分配一个 :ref:`Texture "
"<class_Texture>`。帧ID从0开始，因此第一帧的ID为0，动画的最后一帧的ID为：:ref:`frames "
"<class_AnimatedTexture_property_frames>` - 1。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animatedtexture.rst:131
msgid ""
"You can define any number of textures up to :ref:`MAX_FRAMES "
"<class_AnimatedTexture_constant_MAX_FRAMES>`, but keep in mind that only "
"frames from 0 to :ref:`frames <class_AnimatedTexture_property_frames>` - "
"1 will be part of the animation."
msgstr ""
"您可以定义不超过 :ref:`MAX_FRAMES <class_AnimatedTexture_constant_MAX_FRAMES>` "
"的任意数量的纹理，但请记住，只有从0到 :ref:`frames <class_AnimatedTexture_property_frames>`"
" - 1 的帧，是动画的一部分。"

